{
  "function_path": "netwerk/protocol/http/nsHttpChannel.cpp",
  "function_name": "ContinueProcessResponse1",
  "justification": "This function matches all described behaviors: (1) If mSuspendCount is set, defers processing via mCallOnResume callback and returns immediately; (2) If mCanceled, calls CallOnStartRequest() directly; (3) Reads httpStatus from mResponseHead->Status(); (4) If not proxy connect failed and not 407, processes cookies via CookieVisitor/SetCookieHeaders; (5) Calls ProcessSecurityHeaders() for HSTS/HPKP and logs failures; (6) For httpStatus < 500 and != 421 (not Misdirected Request), calls ProcessAltService(aConnInfo); (7) For httpStatus != 401 and != 407, disconnects and nulls mAuthProvider; (8) If Clear-Site-Data header present, notifies observer service with 'clear-site-data' topic; (9) Proceeds to ContinueProcessResponse2 as next stage."
}

